data.description: **Price Improvement** Well maintained and charming intergenerational home located in highly sought after Del Paso Manor neighborhood.  Good size corner lot with great curb appeal. This wonderful property features a total of five bedrooms and three bathrooms with 2,362 square feet of living space.  Upgraded split system A/C and heater for each individual room along with each containing a keypad lock mechanism. Private family room, master bedroom with balcony overlooking private backyard containing mature fruit trees and good sized storage shed with RV parking.           Great option to run a short term rental for buyers seeking passive income.  This prime location is close to shopping and an easy commute to anywhere in the Sacramento area. A rare find with endless opportunities and a must see to fully appreciate!
